[ProMED-mail would like to thank subscriber John Herbert
<j_a_herbert@yahoo.com> for sending information following a radio
announcement on this advisory.
According to the very thorough investigation of the cases as presented
above, it appears as though the transmission would still qualify as "close
contact" with the chain of transmission being sitting close to an infected
individual on a plane, and then being a member of a tour group that spends
hours together on a daily basis for multiple days. We await further
information from the investigation of this event. - Mod.MPP]
